:0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問有無巴打住過仙石原品の木一の湯<br />\n<br />\n？本身訂咗依間住villa三日兩夜，包早晚餐，但係上網見agoda評價話酒店又多大陸人，夜晚勁嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，夜晚果餐唔好食，咩食shabu shabu好似食牛腩煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n考慮轉Hyatt Regency Hakone Resort &amp; Spa，見佢早餐幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過晚餐要自己揸車出去搵野食。<br />\n如果有巴打住過就俾啲意見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申，四月頭去</blockquote><br />\n我冇記錯就係去呢間<br />\n超正<br />\n落巴士一兩分鐘就到<br />\nd野食又好撚正 秋冬天就shabu 春夏天好似係第2樣<br />\n露天私人風呂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要價錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  22000羊一泊兩食 兩人房<br />\n我全日都唔係好聽到有人嘈 <br />\n第2間未去過唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da625640e8e04b4460cc80db34bcb7a9e30424c","tid":163001,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"七月尾八月頭會同雙親去東京<br />\n佢地想去十日<br />\n諗緊去箱根定河口湖, 還是both<br />\nboth唔知對佢地黎講會唔會太chur"},{"pid":"0a924de0b223ca2ea531b2a4f4f7d5207b7e0b94","tid":163001,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>七月尾八月頭會同雙親去東京<br />\n佢地想去十日<br />\n諗緊去箱根定河口湖, 還是both<br />\nboth唔知對佢地黎講會唔會太chur</blockquote><br />\n住三兩日應該唔chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a35ffc2ce351a86d53ca27d2ef0c3c7d6d5c96b","tid":163001,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>七月尾八月頭會同雙親去東京<br />\n佢地想去十日<br />\n諗緊去箱根定河口湖, 還是both<br />\nboth唔知對佢地黎講會唔會太chur</blockquote><br />\n住三兩日應該唔chur<img sr